  <p>Follow these simple steps to generate your own QR code for free:</p>
  <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-3 mt-4">
    <li><strong>Open the QR Code Generator</strong> &mdash; Visit our <a href="/tools/qr-generator" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">free QR Code Generator tool</a>. No account or sign-up is required.</li>
    <li><strong>Enter your content</strong> &mdash; Type or paste the URL, text, or information you want to encode. For websites, make sure to include the full URL starting with <code>https://</code>.</li>
